==电子签证==
老挝于2019年7月启用电子签证，符合办理落地签证条件的国家的公民可以申请。<ref name="#1">{{cite web |title=LAO OFFICIAL ONLINE VISA |url=https://laoevisa.gov.la/index |accessdate=2019-10-23 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207201221/https://laoevisa.gov.la/index |dead-url=no }}</ref>电子签证有效期为60天，入境老挝后可停留最多30天。电子签证可于3个工作日内签发，签证费视申请人国籍而定。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://en.vietnamplus.vn/laos-launches-evisa-service-in-vientiane/155812.vnp |title=Laos launches e-visa service in Vientiane |access-date=2019-08-04 |archive-date=2019-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710152752/https://en.vietnamplus.vn/laos-launches-evisa-service-in-vientiane/155812.vnp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2019-07/09/c_138212654.htm |title=Lao E-visa launched for foreigners |access-date=2019-08-04 |archive-date=2019-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710123922/http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2019-07/09/c_138212654.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://laoevisa.gov.la/article/Who%20can%20Apply%20for%20Lao%20eVisa |title=Who can Apply for Lao eVisa |access-date=2019-08-04 |archive-date=2019-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731074408/https://laoevisa.gov.la/article/Who%2520can%2520Apply%2520for%2520Lao%2520eVisa |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://laoevisa.gov.la/faq |title=eVisa Laos |access-date=2019-08-04 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924012642/https://laoevisa.gov.la/faq |dead-url=no }}</ref>

电子签证可于在下列口岸入境：<ref name="#1"/>
*[[瓦岱国际机场|瓦岱国际机场]]（[[永珍|永珍]]）
*[[泰寮友誼大橋|泰寮第一友誼大橋]]（[[泰国|泰国]]公路边境）
*[[龍坡邦國際機場|龍坡邦國際機場]]（[[龍坡邦|龍坡邦]]）

对于中老边境口岸，电子签证无法使用。

